spans.text: On ebon throne thou lovest to shroud Thy brows in many a murky cloud
thy train retreat : Thy ruthless host stern Eurus guides , That on a ravenous tiger rides , Dim-figured on whose robe are shown Shipwrecks , and villages overthrown : Grim Auster
